WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.800
mc_aiplayer.

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:07.200
Open source Minecraft AI player for GitHub.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.400
Meet Bob, the fake player who read the job description and took it personally.

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:15.200
You type one goal: mine three diamonds.

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:19.300
The language model understands the request.

00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:24.600
Then deterministic task machines do the real work: gather wood, craft tools, smelt iron, staircase down safely, and keep going until the diamonds show up.

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:29.900
If Bob gets hungry, stuck, attacked, or considers lava soup, the safety net says nope.

00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:34.800
Open the Bob panel, watch health, inventory, task state, and brain status.

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:40.300
mc_aiplayer: LLM plans, tasks execute, Bob survives.
